text: Awesome place for a walk, run or cycling. You will meet so many other people working out on the way. The path is mostly clean and straight. It becomes best if the weather is cloudy
It’s a rocky path, so you should mind your step as you walk down it. But it’s nice that this exists as an option to reach the Green Corridor.
Great access supposed be built by nearby residents, maybe living at Blk 108, a great work! Thank you!
Good access to rail corridor.  Width of ramp could have been wider and better floor finish.
So Happy that this Rail Corridor Access were being built! Now I don't have to climb down dirt paths n in the dark to get to my early morning walks.
